items.title: Severino moved up to start finale vs. Twins
items.summary: The Yankees are prioritizing their pursuit of the Red Sox over a chance to keep the Twins from seeing Luis Severino, shuffling their rotation once again to send their best starter to the mound in Wednesday's series finale at Yankee Stadium.

items.title: Arrieta set to return, slated for Thursday start
items.summary: With the postseason just more than two weeks away, the Cubs will get back a significant piece as they seek their second straight National League Central crown. Jake Arrieta said he will return from a strained right hamstring and start Thursday's critical series opener in Milwaukee.
